WEBVTT

00:10:29.492 --> 00:10:32.671
that promote civility
and reward thoughtfulness.

00:10:33.512 --> 00:10:34.882
I know for a fact

00:10:34.906 --> 00:10:38.122
if I write a post
that is more sensational,

00:10:38.146 --> 00:10:41.657
more one-sided, sometimes
angry and aggressive,

00:10:41.681 --> 00:10:44.452
I get to have more people see that post.

00:10:44.791 --> 00:10:46.480
I will get more attention.

00:10:47.726 --> 00:10:49.990
But what if we put more focus on quality?

00:10:51.149 --> 00:10:52.374
What is more important:

00:10:52.398 --> 00:10:55.051
the total number of readers
of a post you write,

00:10:55.075 --> 00:10:59.696
or who are the people who have impact
that read what you write?